    <h1>Trees</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mb-6">Nievergelt &amp; Hinrichs &middot; Ch. 5 &middot; <a href="https://textbookequity.org/algorithms-and-data-structures/">Algorithms and Data Structures</a></p>

    <div class="bg-zinc-800 rounded-lg p-5 mb-8 callout">
      <p class="text-lg" style="max-width:none">A <strong>binary search tree</strong> keeps keys ordered: left child &lt; parent &lt; right child. Unbalanced, it degrades to a linked list. <strong>AVL trees</strong> restore balance after every insertion. <strong>B-trees</strong> generalize to disk-friendly multi-way branching.</p>
    </div>

